# AgentMaster install profiles
# Format: profile|repo|skill_glob
#   profile    — profile name, selected via `install --profile <name>` or /agent-master profile <name>
#   repo       — a name from repos.manifest, or "agent-master" for this repo's custom skills
#   skill_glob — glob matched against skill directory names ("*" for all skills in the repo)
#
# A repo may appear on multiple lines per profile (one glob each).
# "full" is the implicit default profile: no filtering, everything installs.
# The agent-master orchestrator skill itself is ALWAYS installed, whatever the profile.
# Personal profiles go in ~/.claude/.agentmaster-cache/profiles.local (same format);
# they are merged after this file and survive AgentMaster self-updates.

# dev — code workflow: compression, superpowers discipline, session memory, frontend design, all custom skills
dev|caveman|*
dev|superpowers|*
dev|claude-mem|*
dev|impeccable|*
dev|agent-master|*

# business — domain expertise: compression, claude-skills, orchestrator + repo packing
business|caveman|*
business|claude-skills|*
business|agent-master|agent-master
business|agent-master|repomix-pack

# minimal — orchestrator + compression only
minimal|caveman|*
minimal|agent-master|agent-master
